      <lg type="song lyrics">
        <head>Spliff</head>
        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>Every time someone’s getting </l>
          <l>Into my life </l>
          <l>I find my self just hating </l>
          <l>Everything that he does </l>
          <l>Hope your heart is </l>
          <l>Bigger than mine </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="2" type="stanza">
          <l>I just want you </l>
          <l>To get out of my view </l>
          <l>Take a look at the mirror </l>
          <l>There’s a picture of you </l>
          <l>Promise you that one day I'll wake up </l>
          <l>And destroy all the stuff </l>
          <l>That connects my own self </l>
          <l>To your stupid ideas</l>
        </lg>
      </lg>
